title: Jonathan Elias Says Goodbye to WBZ & Boston - Highlights in HD
description:
WBZ-TV anchor Jonathan Elias anchored his last newscast at the station on May 19, 2015, and said goodbye to viewers.

You can read the story on where he is going here: http://ne1.be/1CxAAiB

Visit NE1 online at: http://www.newenglandone.com
